	"system": {
		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>You touch a bit of bloodhound fur to your nose, heightening your senses and projecting your awareness outside of your body. You can smell a &amp;reference[plant] or animal of your choice in your vicinity.</em></p><p><strong>Ritual Casting Time:</strong> 1 Minute</p><p><strong>Utility Spell</strong></p><p>Describe or name a specific kind of &amp;reference[beast] or &amp;reference[plant]. You don't need line of sight to the target.</p><ul><li><p>You learn the direction and distance to the closest creature or &amp;reference[plant] of that kind within 5 miles, if any are present.</p></li><li><p>If the creature is in motion, you know the direction of its movement.</p></li></ul><p></p><p><strong>*Upcasting:</strong> Range increases by 5 miles for each spell level above 2nd.</p>",
			"chat": ""
		},
